nal|grand final]] against the [[Melbourne Storm]] in front of a record-breaking crowd, with 107,999 people in attendance at the new [[Stadium Australia]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nrl.com/news/2019/09/26/party-like-its-1999-how-storm-upset-dragons-to-kick-off-purple-reign/|title=Party like it's 1999: How Storm upset Dragons to kick off purple reign|date=2019-09-28|website=National Rugby League|language=en|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref>\n\n== Squad Gains and Losses ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:700px;\"\n!{{increase}} or {{decrease}}\n!Player\n!1998 Club\n!1999 Club\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Warren|Carney}}\n|N/A\n| rowspan=\"25\" |{{Leagueicon|St. George Illawarra}} [[St. George Illawarra Dragons]]\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Trent|Barrett}}\n| rowspan=\"12\" |{{Leagueicon|Illawarra}} [[Illawarra Steelers]]\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Craig|Fitzgibbon}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Brad|Mackay}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Paul|McGregor|Paul McGregor (rugby league)}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Craig|Smith|Craig Smith (rugby league, born 1971)}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Shaun|Timmins}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Andrew|Hart|Andrew Hart (rugby league)}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Luke|Patten}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Chris|Leikvoll}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Rod|Wishart}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Jason|Hooper}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Terry|Lamey}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Jamie|Ainscough}}\n| rowspan=\"12\" |{{Leagueicon|St. George}} [[St. George Dragons]]\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Wayne|Bartrim}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Nathan|Blacklock}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Nathan|Brown|Nathan Brown (rugby league, born 1973)}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Mark|Coyne|Mark Coyne (rugby league)}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Anthony|Mundine}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Lee|Murphy}}\n|-\n|{{increase}}\n|{{sortname|Corey|Pearson}}\n|-\n|{{increas